name: About Lines #5: Universe
description:
After the exploration, the universe. The thought world taking shape, unfolding a vast, almost endless space.

This piece is part of a series inspired by Japanese calligraphy and the works of German-French painter Hans Hartung (1904 - 1989).

PNG, 8000 × 5000 px · Original artwork by Andreas Rau · Oslo, 2021
